quran[58]{c,v,t}:
  75,1,Mein qasam khata hun qayamat kay din ki
  75,2,Aur qasam khata hun uss nafas ki jo malamat kernay wala ho
  75,3,Kiya insan yeh khayal kert hai kay hum uss ki hadiyan jama kerengay hi nahi
  75,4,Han zaror kerengay hum to qadir hain kay usski por por tak durust kerdein
  75,5,Bulkay insan to chahta hai kay aagay aagay na farmaniyan kerta jaey
  75,6,Poochata hai kay qayamat ka din kab aaye ga
  75,7,Pus jiss waqat kay nigha pathra jaeygi
  75,8,Aur chand benoor hojaey ga
  75,9,Aur soraj aur chand jama kerdiye jaeingay
  75,10,Uss din insan kahega kay aaj bhegnay ki jagah kahan hai
  75,11,Nahi nahi koi panahgah nahi
  75,12,Aaj to teray perwardigar ki tarf hi qarar gah hai
  75,13,Aaj insan ko uss kay aagay bhejay huye aur peechay choray hoye say aagah kiya jaeyga
  75,14,Bulkay insan khud apney upper aap hujjat hai
  75,15,Agercha kitnay hi bahanay pesh keryga
  75,16,(ay nabi) aap quran ko jadi (yaad kernay)kay liey apni zabaan ko herkat na den
  75,17,Iss ka jama kerna aur (aap ki zaba say)perhna humaray zimmay hai
  75,18,Hum jab issay parhlen to aap iss kay parhnay ki perwi kerein
  75,19,Phir is ka wazeh ker dyna hamary zimy hay
  75,20,Nahi nahi tum jaldi milnay wali(duniya) ki mohabat rakhtay ho
  75,21,Aur akhrat ko chor bethy ho
  75,22,Uss roz bohat say chehery ter o taza aur ba runaq hongay
  75,23,Apney rab ki taraf dekhtay hongay
  75,24,Aur kitnay chehry us din (bad ronaq aur) udas hongay
  75,25,Samjhtay hongay kay in kay sath kamar toor dynay wala mamla ki jaey ga
  75,26,Nahi nahi jab roz hansli tak phunchay gi
  75,27,Aur kaha jaeyga koi char phonk kernay wala hay
  75,28,Aur jan liya unsay kay yeh waqat judai hay
  75,29,Aur pindli say pindli lipat jaey gi
  75,30,Aj tery perwardigar ki taraf chalna hay
  75,31,Us ney na to tasdeeq ki aur na namaz ada ki
  75,32,Bulkay jhutlaya aur roh gatdani ki
  75,33,Phir apney gher walon kay pass itrata hoya gaya
  75,34,Afsos hay tujhay per hasrat hay tujh per
  75,35,Waaye hai aur kharabi hay tery liye
  75,36,Kiya insan yeh samjhta hay kay usy be kaar chor diay jaey ga
  75,37,Kiya wo iki ghary pani ka katra na tha jo tapkaya gaya tha
  75,38,Phir wo laho ka lothra hogay phir Allah ney usy paida kia aur durasat bana diya
  75,39,Phir us say joray yani nar o mada banay
  75,40,kiya (Allah Talah) iss (amar)per qadir nahi kay murday ko zinda kerday
  76,1,Yaqeenan guzra hai insan per ik waqat zamanay mein jab kay yeh koi qabe e zikar chez na tha
  76,2,Besahak hum ney insan ko milay julay nutfay say imtehan kay liye paida kiya aur uss ko sunta dekhta banaya
  76,3,Hum ney ussay raah dikhai abb khua wo shukar guzar banay khua na shukra
  76,4,Yaqeenaa hum ney kafiron kay liye zanjeeron aur toq aur sholon wali aag tayar ker rakhi hay
  76,5,Besahk neek log wo jam piyein gay jiss ki azmaish kafiron ki hay
  76,6,Jo aik chesma hai jiss say Allah kay banday piyen gay uss ki nehrein nikaal ley jaengay (jidher chahen)
  76,7,Jo nazar poori kertay hein aur uss din say dartay hein jiss ki buraee charon taraf phel jaanay wali hia
  76,8,Aur Allah Taalaa ki mohabat mein khana khilatay hein miskeen yateem aur qediyon ko
  76,9,Hum to tumhein sirf Allah Taalaa ki raza mandi kay liye khilatay hein na tum say badla chatay hein na shuker guzari
  76,10,Beshak hum apney perwardigar say uss din ka khof kertay hein jo udaasi aur sakhti wala hoga
  76,11,Pus inhen Allah Taala ney uss din ki buraee say bacha liya aur inhen taazgi aur khushi phonchaee
  76,12,Aut inhen inkay sabar kay badlay jannat aur reshmi libass ata farmaye
  76,13,Yeh wahan takhton per takiey lagaey huye bethen gay na wahan aftab ki garmi dfekhein gay ja jaray ki sakhti
  76,14,In jannaton kay saaye un per jhukey huye hongay aur inkay (meway aur)gunchay neechay latkaaey huye hongay
  76,15,Aur in per chandi kay bartano aur in jaamon ka dor keraya jayega jo sheeshay kay hongay
  76,16,Sheeshy bhi chandi kay jinko(saqi ney)andazay say nap rakha hoga
  76,17,Aur inhein wahan wo jam pilaya jaey ga jin ki amezish zanjabeel ki hogi
  76,18,Jaanat ki ik nehar say jiss ka nam salsabeel hay